conditional recovery from a synthetic stale collateral configuration
├── pool.setUserUseReserveAsCollateral()
│   └── given a synthetic enabled collateral flag with zero scaled balance
│       └── it should revert at the zero-underlying-balance guard and preserve state
├── pool.supply()
│   └── given a synthetic enabled collateral flag with zero scaled balance
│       ├── when supply is below the first floor-mintable amount
│       │   └── it should revert with invalid mint amount and preserve state
│       └── when supply is at the first floor-mintable amount
│           └── it should recover a positive scaled balance [01]
└── pool.setUserUseReserveAsCollateral()
    └── given a synthetic enabled collateral flag with zero scaled balance
        └── given a first-floor-mintable resupply
            └── it should disable collateral [02]
